name: Enrique Gonzalez Churchill Downs
description:
Canvas size:22x23

Anout the artist:
Enrique Gonzalez is a native of Venezuela residing in Kentucky.  He maintains his love of painting in the many images Enrique brings to life on canvas using bright colors and lively brush strokes. His pictures reflect his love of community and animals.  He is most renowed for his equine pictures, especially the ones depicting races at Churchill Downs and Keenland.
